# Dev Test Process Cleanup

Before enabling/running tests in dev mode, always terminate all existing app processes first, then start a fresh new process.

Required sequence:
1. Stop/kill all currently running DouyinVietnamizer/Book Translate app processes.
2. Verify no old process remains active.
3. Start the new dev test process.

Do not run a new dev test instance on top of old running processes.
